 \}\
\
 // --- Countries ---\
 // Front-loaded curve: first listeners tend to span many countries quickly,\
 // then growth slows as the population grows. Using a power curve (^0.4) to reflect this.\
 // At 7am Monday (~4% progress) this gives ~11 countries. By Sunday end, ~41.\
 // Countries: a base value plus a gentle pulse that mimics new countries "arriving"\
